Direct Known Subclasses:
TreeToc
public abstract class TreeTocDragDropImpls
extends JTree
implements Autoscroll

TocTreeDrapDropImpls is an abstract class, it implements the Java drag & drop API to allow a LegendNode change its position by Drag & Drop. Only LegendNode is dragable. When a user selects a LegendNode and start to drag, a "ghost" image of the LegendNode is created. When the drop position is not acceptable, a reject icon will be shown up, otherwise acceptable icon appears. A LegendNode position only can be changed under same parent.
